<l>ceṟāac ciṟucolluñ ceṟṟārpō ṉōkkum </l>
<l>uṟāarpōṉ ṟuṟṟār kuṟippu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Little words that are harsh and looks that are hateful are (but) the expressions of lovers who wish to act like strangers.</l>
